{"tid":1801721,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有老人家竟然覺得自己做廢老係大條道理","createTime":"2019-12-29T00:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T04:31:12.000Z","uid":108894,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a1cb863e85821985930b98169e688e78a35e0435","tid":1801721,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:04:07.000Z","msg":"話說鬆晚我去機場J帶check in counter 開工<br />\n我個掃把叫我去assist個姨姨，我已經心知不妙，因為我知道呢個姨姨唔止工作能力差仲好煩膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係掃把叫落，好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我最初都唔理佢，淨係幫佢啤行李牌<br />\n但佢真係又慢又煩功驚人，我咪出口提醒佢，點樣可以快D簡單D咁，當然都難免有D急躁，因為佢真係令我等到花兒也謝了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢唔止唔聽，仲話: 你以為自己係公司做左年幾，就識飛啦？我同你講，我工作經驗比你多，你咪繼續咁嘅態度對人囉，你遲早係呢度一無所有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同埋我慢係正常，我年紀大咁多又係part timr唔係日日番<br />\n我當堂呆撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，心諗: 我理撚得你之前做野如何，你而家係呢個位做左幾耐呀？有幾多經驗呀？你又做唔做得掂呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好心你唔叻就人地提你就聽下啦。我屌你老味，你真係以為自己係part time同年紀大就大撚晒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做廢老都算，我真係第一次見有人做廢老做得咁大條道理得黎仲人屌番人轉頭<br />\n我下次真係唔想再assist佢，屌第一次試assist仲慘過自己做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次掃把再叫我我一定話唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，爭取自己開counter"},{"pid":"2fd6f5021862a6a9327e7180f21d1640503c1f66","tid":1801721,"uid":101433,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:20:31.000Z","msg":"下次唔好心諗"},{"pid":"79813bbb3135e05557fe146403979d7ebf86663e","tid":1801721,"uid":108894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fd6f5021862a6a9327e7180f21d1640503c1f66","tid":1801721,"uid":101433,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:20:31.000Z","msg":"下次唔好心諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:44:22.000Z","msg":"佢下次再係諗我就屌7佢＋食花生等掃把同佢傾心事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5347316c2db37ba7fc206f634e334c4b08dbd1f0","tid":1801721,"uid":186844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:17:54.000Z","msg":"長命工夫長命做 樓主fg唔識咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d42a3406695eb3bc8f8ed21a3ac0821a72b2c8","tid":1801721,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:30:56.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"939e65a407dbce95b47223add779c860d331c614","tid":1801721,"uid":108894,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5347316c2db37ba7fc206f634e334c4b08dbd1f0","tid":1801721,"uid":186844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T01:17:54.000Z","msg":"長命工夫長命做 樓主fg唔識咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\